---------------------------
-
-  CHANGE LOG - WiiC
-
---------------------------

http://wiic.sf.net


---------------------------
v1.2  --  
---------------------------

	Added:
		-[Mac/Linux] Utility C++ method to enable/disable smoothing for accelerometers
		-[Mac/Linux] wiic-logger now supports timed logging, without any button pressure (useful when you need the device to be still, as for calibration)
		-[Mac/Linux] Added a new C++ method to find and connect to wiimote devices Wii::FindAndConnect()
		-[Mac/Linux] New logging format and support for gyroscope logging		
		-[Mac/Linux] New support for gyroscope logging 
		-[Mac/Linux] Unlimited device search (in case timeout = 0)		
 
	Changed:
		-[Mac/Linux] Different smoothing algorithm, now directly applied to the raw acc values
		-[Mac/Linux] Support for OpenCV 2.2

	Fixed:
		-[Mac/Linux] Fixed raw gravity vector computation

---------------------------
v1.1  --  17 Apr 2011
---------------------------

	Changed:
		-[Mac/Linux] Changed pitch and roll computation
		-[Mac/Linux] Changed the default smooth parameter for pitch and roll computation

	Fixed:
		-[Mac] Memory leak in Wiimote read

---------------------------
v1.00 --  11 Apr 2011
---------------------------

	Added:
		-[Mac/Linux] Wiimote logging system
		-[Mac/Linux] WiiC machine learning module

---------------------------
v0.53 -- 01 Sep 2010
---------------------------

	Added:
		-[Mac/Linux] Wiimote registration system
		-[Mac/Linux] WiiC configuration folder (.wiic)
		-[Mac/Linux] New Wiimote loading function ("wiic_load" for C and "CWii::LoadRegisteredWiimotes()" for C++)

---------------------------
v0.51 -- 21 Aug 2010
---------------------------

	Added:
		-[Mac/Linux] Motion Plus gyroscope threshold can be set by the user

	Changed:
		-[Mac/Linux] "wiiuse" prefix is not anymore used, everything starts with "wiic"
		-[Mac/Linux] Usual optimizations

---------------------------
v0.50 -- 08 Jul 2010
---------------------------

	Added:
		- [Mac/Linux] Full Balance Board support

---------------------------
v0.40 -- 17 May 2010
---------------------------

	Fixed:
		- [Mac] Fix for IOBluetoothHostController 
		- [Mac] wiiuse_poll is now non-blocking on Mac platforms too

	Changed:
		- [Linux/Mac] Removed old Windows stuff
		- [Mac] Changed environment variable

---------------------------
v0.31 -- 25 Feb 2010
---------------------------

	Fixed:
		- [Mac] Motion Plus bug
		- [Mac] Now NSRunLoop is used instead of CFRunLoop
		- [Mac] Pressing the power button on the Wiimote now works

---------------------------
v0.30 -- 19 Feb 2010
---------------------------

	Added:
		- [Linux/Mac] WiiC now adopts CMake compiling system

---------------------------
v0.22 -- 09 Feb 2010
---------------------------

	Changed:
		- No more Windows support

	Added:
		- [Linux/Mac] WiiC now embeds WiiuseCpp

---------------------------
v0.21 -- 13 Jan 2010
---------------------------

	Changed:
		- [Linux/Mac/Win] New organization within header files 

---------------------------
v0.20 -- 11 Jan 2010
---------------------------

	Added:
		- WiiC now supports Motion Plus (without supporting other extensions attached to it)

---------------------------
v0.14 -- 17 Dec 2009
---------------------------

	Fixed:
		- [Linux/Mac/Win] Fixed a bug of Wiiuse about rumble
		- [Linux/Mac/Win] Fixed a bug of Wiiuse in wiiuse_disconnect
	
	Changed:
		- [Linux/Mac/Win] The rumble is managed only in wiiuse_send() and not
				  anymore in other functions

---------------------------
v0.13 -- 14 Dec 2009
---------------------------

	Added:
		- WiiC now supports Mac platforms

